translate spanish Epilogue_Villain_Kyou_daac9247:

    # "Anyway, as one final test I grab [p_their] wrist and take [p_their] pulse again. It seems to be just as stable and even as when I took it before."
    "Como sea, como una última prueba, tomo su muñeca y reviso su pulso una vez más. Perece estar igual de estable y equilibrado que la vez anterior."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:640
