translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_1caaddf7:

    # n sad "Uh, sure..." with dissolve
    n sad "Eh, claro..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:4435
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_446cd0ad:

    # "As she nods, Nozomi seems to spy the two chairs I have beside me, arranged a few feet apart. " with dissolve
    "Asintiendo, Nozomi parece espiar las dos sillas que tengo a mi lado, puestas a poco más de un metro una de la otra." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3082
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_3d9f1ca8:

    # "I swear I just saw Nozomi's eyes glimmer as I turn my attention back to the task at hand."
    "Podría jurar que vi los ojos de Nozomi iluminarse, mientras devuelvo mi atención a la tarea en cuestión."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3083
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_551c1eb7:

    # ks "Now, there's all kinds of ways you can hypnotize someone."
    ks "Pues bien, hay toda clase de formas de hipnotizar a alguien."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3084
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_d70ac7c1:

    # ks "Like, you can get them to focus on something like a pocketwatch, or you can have them lie back and relax really deeply."
    ks "Como hacer que se concentre en algo como un reloj de bolsillo, o que se recueste y se relaje muy profundamente."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3088
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_6904c0fd:

    # ks "But what I'm going to do with Sayori is... well, first I'm gonna need her hand." with dissolve
    ks "Pero lo que voy a hacer con Sayori es... bueno, primero necesito su mano." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3089
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_b0c14518:

    # "Sayori knows what's coming of course, so she offers me her hand immediately for me to take."
    "Sayori sabe muy bien lo que está por venir, así que me ofrece su mano de inmediato."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3090
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_05cd0c15:

    # ks "Cool. Now Sayori, I need your arm too. So if you could just let it go completely limp for me?"
    ks "Genial. Voy a necesitar tu brazo también, Sayori. Así que, ¿podrías aflojarlo, por favor?"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3091
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7a1c57f8:

    # "I can feel her arm loosen up as I start to swing her hand gently back and forth while I try to address those watching as clearly as I can."
    "Puedo sentir cómo su brazo se relaja mientras balanceo suavemente su mano e intento dirigirme a quienes nos miran con tanta claridad como me es posible."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3092
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_b0e6b420:

    # ks "Great, so now I'm going to pull her arm around like so. And Akiko, I need you to be ready to catch her, okay?"
    ks "Grandioso, ahora voy a sacudir su mano justo así. Y, Akiko, necesito que estés lista para atraparla, ¿de acuerdo?"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3093
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_9b9cde35:

    # a surprised "Y-you mean I... o-o-okay!" with dissolve
    a surprised "¿D-dices que yo...? ¡E-e-está bien!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3094
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_cd2149b6:

    # "As Akiko tenses in anticipation I start to pull Sayori's arm more aggressively. First in a left to right motion, then going in a circle then straight up and down..."
    "Akiko se tensa con anticipación y yo empiezo a mover el brazo de Sayori con más agresividad. Primero de lado a lado, luego en círculos y después de arriba a abajo."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3095
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_d48a4f95:

    # "And while I do that, my free hand reaches above Sayori's face as I start to make a spidering motion with my fingers."
    "Y mientras lo hago, mi mano libre se eleva por encima del rostro de Sayori y empiezo a mover los dedos como araña."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3099
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e74b7146:

    # ks "Now just follow the path of my fingers, Sayori. Follow them..." with dissolve
    ks "Ahora sigue el movimiento de mis dedos, Sayori. Síguelos..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:4462
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_32e19af2:

    # "I say that more for the benefit of those watching as she's already tracking my fingers dancing in her face, seemingly unconcerned with my messing with her arm."
    "Lo digo más que nada para la audiencia, pues Sayori ya está atenta a la danza de mis dedos, aparentemente sin preocuparse por lo que hago con su brazo."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3101
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_eafa71b7:

    # ks "That's right, following my fingers, focusing on them while also standing up nice and straight."
    ks "Eso es, sigue mis dedos, concéntrate en ellos y a la vez mantente firmemente de pie."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3102
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_6fe85b3d:

    # "Sayori suggested I impress that last part to her during rehearsals and yeah, I see her point about that."
    "Sayori sugirió que le indicara esa última parte durante los ensayos, y sí, creo que tiene sentido."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3103
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_123e2c1c:

    # "Especially with what we're about to show the class."
    "Sobre todo con lo que estamos a punto de mostrarle a la clase."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3104
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_5ec273f6:

    # ks frown "Standing straight while watching up and down, round and round and -{w=0.5}{nw}"
    ks frown "Firmemente de pie y mirando de arriba a abajo, dando vueltas y vueltas y- {w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3110
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_c4064df4:

    # extend "SLEEP! Relaxing now deeper and deeper. {w=0.5}{nw}"
    extend "¡DUERME! Profundamente relajada. {w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3112
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_d3a6d439:

    # extend "Deep in trance now, Sayori."
    extend "En un trance muy profundo, Sayori."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3113
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_d1b163e9:

    # "Just as I mouthed the word \"sleep\", I tugged her arm down sharply as I transitioned the hand in front of her to snapping my fingers as quickly as I could."
    "Justo en cuanto dije la palabra \"duerme\", jalé bruscamente su brazo hacia abajo, y chasqueé los dedos que tengo delante de ella tan rápido como pude."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3114
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_ff3a4a11:

    # "Akiko tensed in fright as I raised my voice, hands raised by Sayori's shoulders, but it seems she needn't have bothered."
    "Akiko se puso tensa del susto cuando alcé la voz, subiendo las manos hasta la altura de los hombros de Sayori, pero parece que no fue necesario."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3115
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_9372fd67:

    # ks smile "So did you guys see that? How I was moving her arm around and twinkling my fingers in her eyes?"
    ks smile "¿Vieron eso, chicos? ¿Cómo estaba moviendo su brazo y revoloteando mis dedos en sus ojos?"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3116
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_24c48d28:

    # n neutral "{size=15}A butterfly induction.{/size}" with dissolve
    n neutral "{size=15}Una inducción de la mariposa.{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3117
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_f9102d3c:

    # a neutral_side "Hm?" with dissolve
    a neutral_side "¿Mm?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3118
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_13586982:

    # n sad_closed blush "Oh, n-nothing." with dissolve
    n sad_closed blush "Oh, n-nada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3119
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_8fdbb75e:

    # ks "All that stuff occupies the mind, especially if you have to focus on it like Sayori did."
    ks "Todo eso mantiene ocupada a la mente, en especial si tienes que concentrarte en ello, como Sayori."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3122
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_238a7c4a:

    # ks "So when I tugged her arm and told her to sleep, it gave her mind something clear and easy to focus on." with dissolve
    ks "Así que, cuando tiré de su brazo y le dije que durmiera, le dio a su mente algo claro y simple en lo cual concentrarse." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3123
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_dbcf2b10:

    # a sad "So she fell asleep standing up?" with dissolve
    a sad "¿Y se durmió de pie?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3124
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_93196172:

    # "Ah, that spoiled my rhythm. Sayori warned me I could get questions while I was doing this."
    "Ay, me estropeó el ritmo. Sayori me advirtió que podría recibir preguntas mientras hacía esto."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3125
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_eedc8e91:

    # "Just gotta deal with it head on."
    "Pues tendré que lidiar con ello."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3127
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_26bbc28e:

    # ks sigh "It's not like she's literally asleep; she's just on a different level of consciousness right now. She can still hear us." with dissolve
    ks sigh "No es que literalmente esté dormida; simplemente está en un nivel distinto de consciencia. Aún puede oírnos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3128
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_bf12a56f:

    # ks "And when you're in this state of hypnosis you can become really suggestible, and you can use it to achieve some awesome things."
    ks "Y cuando te encuentras en este estado de hipnosis, puedes volverte muy sugestionable, y puedes usar eso para lograr cosas alucinantes."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3129
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_30a2ea4f:

    # "I then turn back to Sayori as I reach up to touch the top of her head."
    "Y entonces vuelvo a encarar a Sayori, tocando la parte de arriba de su cabeza."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3130
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_1204bb04:

    # ks smile "For example..."
    ks smile "Por ejemplo..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3131
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_9e017b8e:

    # "I need to move on quickly."
    "Debo moverme rápido."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3132
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_96305997:

    # ks "Sayori, I want you to just imagine now that your body is becoming incredibly rigid. From the top of your head, your neck..."
    ks "Sayori, quiero que imagines que tu cuerpo se pone extremadamente rígido. Comenzando por tu cabeza, tu cuello..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3133
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_4b9677ff:

    # "I then reach down to pat her shoulders, then her forearms as the class watches me curiously."
    "Luego pongo las manos en sus hombros, posteriormente en sus antebrazos, mientras la clase observa con curiosidad."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3136
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_a89bc09a:

    # ks "Your shoulders and arms, your chest; all as if there's a strong metal bar running all the way through you. Totally stiff, totally immovable." with dissolve
    ks "Tus hombros y brazos, tu torso; como si te atravesara una fuerte barra de metal. Completamente tiesa, completamente inmóvil." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3137
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_2e0339a4:

    # "Next I tap the sides of her calves and the tops of her feet before moving to pat her arms and head again."
    "Después toco los costados de sus pantorrillas y sus pies, para luego regresar a sus brazos y su cabeza."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3138
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_8b719c87:

    # ks "Your legs, your feet, all made of metal. Every muscle in your body, your chest, everything, completely stiff, totally unable to move in any way."
    ks "Tus piernas, tus pies, totalmente hechos de metal. Cada músculo de tu cuerpo, tu torso, todo. Completamente rígido, totalmente incapaz de moverte."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3139
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e8a77c77:

    # "Feeling her arm gently, it sure feels like Sayori's ready for the real show to begin."
    "Al palpar gentilmente su brazo, puedo sentir que Sayori está lista para dar comienzo al verdadero espectáculo."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3140
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_1b7deb61:

    # ks "{size=15}Can you hold her shoulders now, Akiko? We're going to carry her.{/size}"
    ks "{size=15}¿Puedes sujetarla de los hombros ahora, Akiko? Vamos a cargarla.{/size}"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3142
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_65da3202:

    # "Akiko's eyes widen, but after being teased with the prospect of having to hold Sayori enough times I think she's ready for this." with dissolve
    "Akiko me mira sorprendida, pero después de sugerir tantas veces la idea de sostener a Sayori, creo que está lista." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3145
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_fc36ead5:

    # "And as she puts her hands to Sayori's shoulderblades I turn to instruct Nozomi only to see her nod at me and look to Sayori's feet." with dissolve
    "Y mientras le pone las manos en los hombros, me preparo para darle instrucciones a Nozomi, pero ella asiente de inmediato y voltea a ver los pies de Sayori." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3146
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_877245e2:

    # "She seems to know what's up, so with Akiko ready I give Sayori a gentle push into the waiting hands of our student council president."
    "Parece que sabe lo que está pasando, así que, con Akiko en posición, le doy a Sayori un ligero empujón, dejándola caer en las manos de nuestra presidenta del consejo estudiantil."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3148
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_8b7d0b84:

    # "There's a hushed gasp among the audience, and from Akiko herself as Sayori falls stiffly backwards against her while she strains from the weight." with dissolve
    "Se escucha un silencioso resuello en la audiencia, y también uno de Akiko, azotada por el peso de Sayori, quien cae de espaldas sobre ella." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3149
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_220a6796:

    # "Watching Akiko so out of her depth is a little fun, but I have work to do myself, as I place my arms underneath Sayori's lower back and thighs..."
    "Es un tanto divertido ver a Akiko tan confundida, pero tengo trabajo que hacer, así que coloco mis brazos debajo de la espalda de Sayori."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3150
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_dfa006a8:

    # "... and Nozomi reaches down to grab her friend's ankles before we collectively heave Sayori's rigid body up in the air."
    "... y con Nozomi levantando los tobillos de su amiga, tenemos el rígido cuerpo de Sayori en el aire."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3151
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_73b42f57:

    # ks happy "Haha, see how rigid she is? It's like she really thinks she's made of iron or something!"
    ks happy "Jaja, ¿ven lo rígida que está? ¡Como si de verdad creyera que está hecha de hierro o algo!"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3152
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_6524799a:

    # a surprised "Rrrrgh, K-Kyouuu I'm gonna drop her!" with dissolve
    a surprised "¡Ayyy, K-Kyouuu, se me cae!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3153
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_1ea51b50:

    # ks smile "Okay, okay, c'mon just set her down here."
    ks smile "Muy bien, muy bien, vengan, pónganla aquí."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3154
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7063bdc2:

    # "And with that the three of us carefully move backwards towards the waiting chairs before we set her down."
    "Y dicho eso, los tres retrocedemos cuidadosamente hacia las sillas y la bajamos."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3155
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_9545f6bb:

    # "Sayori's head rests on one chair, the heels of her feet on the other as we let her go. The rest of her body forming a perfect, straight bridge between the two."
    "La cabeza de Sayori descansa sobre una silla, sus talones sobre la otra, y finalmente la soltamos. Su cuerpo forma así un puente recto entre las dos."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3156
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_cc1b5758:

    # a "A-and she's just going to lay like that?"
    a "¿Y a-así se va a quedar?"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3157
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_cb4597f9:

    # "I nod triumphantly to Akiko before addressing the crowd."
    "Asiento triunfantemente para Akiko, y luego me dirijo a la audiencia."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3158
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_13ef9522:

    # ks "Yeah, so what Sayori's experiencing now is full body catalepsy. She's in a state of rigidity that she just wouldn't be able to accomplish were she conscious."
    ks "Sí. Lo que Sayori experimenta ahora es catalepsia de cuerpo completo."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3224
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_ae5a625f:

    # "And by way of emphasising my point, I push down gently on Sayori's stomach as everyone watches." with dissolve
    "Y para enfatizar ese punto, presiono suavemente el estómago de Sayori, mientras todos observan." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3160
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_ebae1c42:

    # ks "That's just how powerful the hypnotic state can be. You could even sit on her and she'd take your full weight!"
    ks "Así de poderoso es este estado. ¡Incluso podrías sentarte sobre ella y aguantaría tu peso!"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3161
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_ad87d3dd:

    # "There's a few gasps, from Akiko as well as those watching, although as I spare a glance at the adults in the room I quickly add:"
    "Jadeos brotan, tanto de Akiko como del público, aunque tras darles un vistazo a los adultos que hay en el aula, me apresuro a añadir:"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3162
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e9da140b:

    # ks happy blush "B-but we're not gonna be testing that tonight, haha! You'll just have to take my word for it."
    ks happy blush "¡P-pero, no vamos a poner eso a prueba hoy, jaja! Tendrán que creer en mi palabra."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3229
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_501c3903:

    # "Yeah, I think I'm already pushing my luck as it is with some of the more concerned authority figures in the room. I think I'd better wrap this up." with dissolve
    "Sí, creo que ya estoy tentando mucho mi suerte con las preocupadas figuras de autoridad del salón. Creo que mejor ya doy cierre." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3164
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_2f4836c2:

    # ks smile noblush "Anyway, I think we'd better get Sayori back on her feet, okay, ladies?"
    ks smile noblush "En fin, creo que será mejor que pongamos a Sayori de pie, ¿de acuerdo, señoritas?"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3168
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_fe92b695:

    # ks "Waking in one... two... {w=0.5}{nw}"
    ks "Despierta en uno... dos... {w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3171
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_565bbceb:

    # extend "three, Sayori. Wide awake and alert and refreshed."
    extend "tres, Sayori. Completamente despierta, fresca y alerta."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3172
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_9d6745ca:

    # "Sayori blinks herself back into consciousness, to the relief of some in the audience it seems."
    "Sayori pestañea mientras recupera el conocimiento, para el alivio de algunos en la audiencia, al parecer."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3173
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_a8766284:

    # ks "Hey, Sayori. How are we doing?"
    ks "¿Qué tal, Sayori? ¿Cómo estás?"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3174
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_0931f672:

    # s "I... am good."
    s "Eh... estoy bien."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3176
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_05410d3b:

    # "She blinks a few more times, registering all the eyes on her before turning to smile." with dissolve
    "Parpadea un par de veces más, vislumbrado todos los ojos que tiene ante ella para luego sonreír." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3177
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_c814eca9:

    # s "From the looks on their faces, it would seem the demonstration was a success."
    s "Por la mirada en sus caras, diría que la demostración fue todo un éxito."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3178
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_ffc40c88:

    # ks smile "Oh yeah, it worked without a hitch."
    ks smile "Oh, sí, funcionó sin problemas."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3181
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_4a84753c:

    # "And with that, Sayori turns to Akiko with a grin." with dissolve
    "Y con eso, Sayori se vuelve hacia Akiko con una mueca." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3182
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_92cd10d3:

    # a "Wh-what?"
    a "¿Qu-qué?"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3183
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_28e9895a:

    # s "Thank you. For having my back."
    s "Gracias. Por cuidarme la espalda."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3184
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e488693d:

    # a sigh "Y-yeah, of course, Sayori. Always." with dissolve
    a sigh "S-sí, por supuesto, Sayori. Cuando sea." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3186
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_b7360e7f:

    # "She then turns to the class and gives them a bow." with dissolve
    "Después voltea a ver a la clase y da una reverencia." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3187
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_1c8802b8:

    # s uniform alert_sleep "And thank you all for coming out." with dissolve
    s uniform alert_sleep "Y gracias a todos por venir." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3188
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7c53c400:

    # s alert_smile_right "I regret that we had so little time to demonstrate what hypnosis is capable of, or give a more in-depth explanation..." with dissolve
