    # ks "At least until I dismantled that thing."
    ks "Al menos hasta que desmantelé esa cosa."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3341
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_84681880:

    # s uniform_folded "And I maintain that was the correct thing to do, Kyou." with dissolve
    s uniform_folded "Y reitero que eso fue lo correcto, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3342
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_cdba9c95:

    # s alert_smile "But it is interesting... After all, a good hypnotist needs to be in tune with those they intend to hypnotize." with dissolve
    s alert_smile "Pero es interesante... Después de todo, un buen hipnotista debe estar en sintonía con aquellos a quienes pretende hipnotizar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3343
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_4217e5a7:

    # s alert_smile_right "If they cannot build a comfortable rapport, and speak clearly and confidently, then they cannot hope to achieve what they intended." with dissolve
    s alert_smile_right "Si no puede crear una cómoda conexión, y hablar claramente y con confianza, no podrá lograr su cometido." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:4714
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_3588c9a7:

    # s uniform_handup "So perhaps that truly was all you needed: A commitment to a soft science to round out the edges of your personality." with dissolve
    s uniform_handup "Así que, quizá eso fue lo que te hacía falta: Comprometerte a una ciencia blanda para así pulir tu personalidad." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3345
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_608c5624:

    # ks sigh "Eh, whatever."
    ks sigh "Eh, como sea."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3346
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_a0598076:

    # s uniform_folded alert_sleep "I think you could take it further." with dissolve
    s uniform_folded alert_sleep "Creo que podrías llevarlo más allá." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3347
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_6dffe5c4:

    # ks surprised "Huh?"
    ks surprised "¿Eh?"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3348
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_818e13ab:

    # s alert_concerned_right "Why do you look so perturbed? I honestly have not seen you as fulfilled as you are now." with dissolve
    s alert_concerned_right "¿Por qué luces tan perturbado? Francamente nunca te vi tan realizado como ahora." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3349
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7e9ed63f:

    # ks "But... Sayori, this isn't what I wanted to do with my life! I wanted to work in tech."
    ks "Pero... Sayori, ¡esto no es lo que quería hacer con mi vida! YO quería trabajar en la tecnología."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3350
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_5d142b1d:

    # "Yeah. That's all I wanted to do."
    "Sí. Eso es lo que quería."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3351
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_70ea99d4:

    # ks frown "I mean, sure being a hypnotist is interesting, and getting to put people into a trance and have fun with them or try to help is kind of a thrill."
    ks frown "Es que, claro, ser hipnotista es interesante, y poner a la gente en trance y divertirme o intentar ayudarla sí es emocionante."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3352
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_0e2fb6dd:

    # ks "With you especially, but..."
    ks "Sobre todo contigo, pero..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3354
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_2850c273:

    # s alert_pout_closed blush "Well, far be it for me to dictate your career for you, but I do feel you have developed a passion for this." with dissolve
    s alert_pout_closed blush "Bueno, no está en mis manos decidir tu carrera por ti, pero en verdad siento que has desarrollado pasión por esto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3355
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e5a9fa9b:

    # s alert_pout "And your career aspirations for the tech world seem... somewhat directionless, if you don't mind me saying so." with dissolve
    s alert_pout "Y tus aspiraciones de carrera en el mundo de la tecnología no parecen... tener rumbo, a decir verdad, si me permites decirlo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3356
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_917f2ed1:

    # s uniform alert_concerned_right noblush "I only ask that you do not dismiss it so readily." with dissolve
    s uniform alert_concerned_right noblush "Solo te pido que no lo descartes tan prontamente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3357
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_2be8a288:

    # ks sigh "Sure... I'll think about it, I guess."
    ks sigh "Claro... Lo pensaré, supongo."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3358
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_79b0dedd:

    # "But I think we're getting sidetracked here."
    "Pero creo que nos estamos descarrilando."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3359
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_eec2c302:

    # ks smirk "But this is so like you, isn't it."
    ks smirk "Pero esto es típico de ti, ¿no?"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3360
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7d9ca0a3:

    # s alert_surprised_right "Huh? What is?" with dissolve
    s alert_surprised_right "¿Eh? ¿Qué cosa?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3361
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_94a49cb2:

    # ks "We came here to relax and already you're stressing out worrying about me!"
    ks "¡Vinimos aquí a relajarnos y ya te estás estresando preocupándote por mí!"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3362
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_b0c1b9d4:

    # s uniform_folded alert_sleeptalk_concerned "Ugh. It is not just you. I worry about all of you." with dissolve
    s uniform_folded alert_sleeptalk_concerned "Aj. No solo por ti. Me preocupo por todos ustedes." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3363
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_a35ca2a4:

    # s uniform "I worry that it was too late to reorganize my life with our entrance examinations so imminent." with dissolve
    s uniform "Me preocupa que haya sido muy tarde para reorganizar mi vida con nuestros exámenes de admisión tan inminentes." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3364
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_2a3b37c2:

    # s "And..."
    s "Y..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3365
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_a8640b46:

    # ks neutral "You're worried about us?"
    ks neutral "¿Te preocupas por nosotros?"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3366
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_53273aab:

    # s uniform_folded alert_sleeptalk blush "..." with dissolve
    s uniform_folded alert_sleeptalk blush "..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:4579
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_06b6c3f4:

    # "Oh, man. She really has thought about it. But if she's set on making it into med school then how can I..."
    "Oh, cielos. Sí lo ha pensado. Pero si irá a la escuela de medicina, ¿cómo puedo yo..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3368
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_57143df4:

    # "No, this isn't the time to be thinking about this stuff right now."
    "No, ahora no es tiempo de pensar en esas cosas."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3369
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_4a17fa7b:

    # ks "There'll be another time where you can worry about all of that, Sayori. A better time."
    ks "Ya habrá tiempo de preocuparte por todo eso, Sayori. Todo a su tiempo."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3441
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_a63babbc:

    # s "I... don't necessarily disagree. But here?"
    s "No... discrepo necesariamente. Pero ¿aquí?"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3371
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_b2c7a912:

    # ks smile "Right now it's doll time."
    ks smile "Ahora mismo es tiempo de muñeca."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3445
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_3c04fc25:

    # s "{size=15}Ahh...{/size}"
    s "{size=15}Aah...{/size}"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3373
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_f1447fef:

    # "Sayori was right about getting me to let go of that penlight."
    "Sayori tenía razón en que debía dejar ir esa linterna."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3374
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_69b6a66a:

    # ks "That's right. Doll time. It's alright to let your worries slip away when it's doll time. Letting everything turn to plastic when it's doll time."
    ks "Eso es. Tiempo de muñeca. Puedes dejar que ir tus preocupaciones cuando es tiempo de muñeca. Que todo se vuelva plástico cuando es tiempo de muñeca."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3375
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7783c5cb:

    # "And not just because it was dangerous. It turned out I really didn't need it. Especially not in her case."
    "Y no solo porque fuera peligrosa. Resultó que no la necesitaba. Sobre todo, no en su caso."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3376
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_2db8f8b0:

    # "The amount of suggestibility she has, to say nothing of her trust in me; it's pretty incredible."
    "Con lo sugestionable que es, sin mencionar la confianza que tiene en mí; es en serio increíble."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3452
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_be918fc0:

    # "So now, taking her hands gently in mine, I slowly unfold them before pulling them down to rest stiffly at her sides."
    "Y ahora, tomando sus manos con gentileza, las despliego lentamente y las bajo hasta sus costados."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3379
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_81fc664d:

    # ks "No cares. No concerns... just plastic."
    ks "Sin miedos. Sin preocupaciones... Solo plástico."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3455
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_18f9bb72:

    # "Cupping a hand on her chin, I then slowly lift and tilt her head to face straight. She'd be looking right at me if her eyelids hadn't shuttered." with dissolve
    "Colocando una mano en su barbilla, levanto e inclino suavemente su cabeza, haciendo que mire hacia adelante. Estaría mirándome de no haber cerrado sus ojos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3381
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_27905c36:

    # "She looks so perfect. And with her brow having uncreased from the suggested mindlessness, so worry free."
    "Luce tan perfecta. Sus cejas completamente relajadas, estando libre de mente, libre de preocupaciones."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3382
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_9714e50f:

    # ks "So I was thinking, Sayori... You can stay a few minutes like this, nothing but plastic on your mind, allowing yourself to enjoy that feeling."
    ks "Se me ocurrió, Sayori... que podrías quedarte así unos minutos, sin más que plástico en tu mente, disfrutando de ese sentimiento."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3383
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_eb69b631:

    # ks "Just for a little while. And then, we can go back out there and enjoy the rest of the festival together; just having a nice, relaxing time."
    ks "Solo por un rato. Y luego, podemos salir y gozar del resto del festival juntos; pasar el tiempo con alegría y relajarnos."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3384
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_8d9bd10f:

    # ks "Does that sound good to you, Sayori?"
    ks "¿Suena bien, Sayori?"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3385
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_3fd9a030:

    # "I stand there, smiling at her serenity, as I await her response."
    "Me quedo de pie, sonriendo ante su serenidad, esperando su respuesta."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3387
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_d7da6e07:

    # "And then she smiles..." with dissolve
    "Y entonces, ella sonríe..." with dissolve
# TODO: Translation updated at 2020-11-30 19:20

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3495
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_27a4f6b0:

    # "It's been several weeks after Kyou's fateful false confession."
    "Han pasado varias semanas desde la fatídica confesión falsa de Kyou."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3496
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_050996f1:

    # "He confirms that he's no longer allowed on school grounds, and he got the mother of all scoldings from his dad when he heard about it."
    "Confirma que ya no se le permite la entrada en las instalaciones de la escuela, y recibió la madre de todos los regaños de su padre cuando se enteró."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3497
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_602b0ba1:

    # "It's all feeling so hopeless..."
    "Se siente que no hay esperanza..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3498
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_e2efb6ca:

    # "So this morning Kyou's basically just staring up at the ceiling in his room. Feeling dead to the world."
    "Esta mañana Kyou tan solo está mirando el techo en su habitación. Sintiéndose muerto por dentro."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3502
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_001c7be8:

    # "As he ponders about his life choices, his phone rings..."
    "Mientras reflexiona las elecciones de su vida, su teléfono suena..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3503
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_43991a56:

    # "Who on earth could be... Akiko?!"
    "¿Quién podrá...? ¡¿Akiko?!"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3505
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_1aa2fad8:

    # "Yeah, Kyou's VERY surprised that she wants to talk to him again."
    "Sí, Kyou está MUY sorprendido de que quiera hablarle otra vez."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3506
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_3604b439:

    # "And Akiko responds to his bewilderment by saying she knows the truth about what happened. Risa couldn't stand to see Akiko as she was and saw fit to tell her."
    "Y Akiko responde a su desconcierto diciendo que sabe lo que realmente pasó. Risa no pudo soportar a Akiko en su estado, y le pareció apropiado contarle."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3507
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_ab741c94:

    # "Akiko's been suffering herself you see, having been stigmatized for speaking out in support of Kyou before."
    "Akiko también ha estado sufriendo, habiendo sido estigmatizada por haber apoyado a Kyou."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3508
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_8c16ecd0:

    # "Kyou's like, oh shit, she's someone ELSE he's fucked over, isn't she? But Akiko shrugs off his apologies. He can't control people being jerks."
    "Kyou responde, oh mierda, a ella TAMIBÉN le jodió la vida, ¿no es cierto? Pero Akiko le dice que no se disculpe. No puede evitar que la gente sea idiota."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3509
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_59b8e1e1:

    # "Plus it did help to know that her faith in Kyou turned out to be justified. It's helped to keep her going."
    "Además, ayudó saber que su fe en Kyou sí estaba justificada. La ha ayudado a seguir adelante."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3510
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_419d6775:

    # "But more to the point, she wants to see him again."
    "Pero yendo al grano, quiere volver a verlo."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3511
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_ef1e3c0d:

    # "And after being relieved of the student council presidency by popular vote, she has some time freed up, and now she's walking around town trying to de-stress."
    "Y tras ser relevada de la presidencia del consejo estudiantil por voto popular, tiene un poco de tiempo libre, y ahora está caminando por la calle, intentando desestresarse."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3513
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_86d5d01f:

    # "So could she come visit? If it's not inconvenient? She's not far from his house, actually..."
    "Así que, ¿podría pasar de visita? ¿No será mucha molestia? No está lejos de su casa, de hecho..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3517
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_a85e41a3:

    # "Kyou perks up at the prospect of seeing her again, and he has just enough time to freshen up before she shows up at his door with a brave smile on her face."
    "La esperanza de volverla a ver le levanta a Kyou el ánimo, y tiene justo el tiempo suficiente de refrescarse antes de que llegue a su puerta con una valiente sonrisa en su rostro."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3519
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_f9b3d131:

    # "Never mind her, though. She wants to know how HE's doing!" with dissolve
    "Pero no hablemos de ella. ¡Quiere saber cómo le va a ÉL!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3520
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_6045d599:

    # "Kyou admits he's been going through the motions, studying for his entrance exams at home and getting a little tutelage from his former classmate Sayori."
    "Kyou admite que simplemente a seguido la rutina, estudiando para sus exámenes de admisión y recibiendo algo de tutela de su excompañera de clase, Sayori."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3522
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_38940842:

    # "But it's hard. He fears for his future." with dissolve
    "Pero es difícil. Teme por su futuro." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3523
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_401f0ea8:

    # "Akiko mentions she heard Hiroko is being re-evaluated by the scholarships board after her appeal was successful, so it's in her hands now."
    "Akiko menciona que oyó que Hiroko será reevaluada por la junta escolar de becas luego de que su apelación tuvo éxito, así ahora queda en sus manos."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3524
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_22d2c2f2:

    # "Kyou confirms he heard the same from Sayori, who it seems is his point of contact with the other girls."
    "Kyou confirma que escuchó lo mismo de Sayori, quien parece ser su punto de contacto con las otras chicas."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3526
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_c5c31dcf:

    # "As for Kyou's future? Akiko gives a similar speech to when they first met. He's taken another huge tumble and things are going to suck." with dissolve
    "¿En cuanto al futuro de Kyou? Akiko le da un discurso similar a cuando se conocieron. Ha sufrido una enorme caída, y será bastante malo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3527
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_9c87a9ea:

    # "But they WILL get better. Face adversity, bow, ready your sword..."
    "Pero SÍ mejorará. Encara a la adversidad, haz una reverencia, prepara tu espada..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3529
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_9488871f:

    # "You've already learned so much from your failings, Kyou. You've got this." with dissolve
    "Ya has aprendido mucho de tus fracasos, Kyou. Puedes hacerlo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3531
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_80bc3c9b:

    # "Honestly, Kyou's a little overcome by the fact Akiko is here and still gives a shit. But he also remembers Akiko's suffering." with dissolve
    "Honestamente, Kyou está un poco abrumado por el hecho de que Akiko esté aquí y aún le importa una mierda. Pero también recuerda que Akiko está sufriendo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3532
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_e66aef90:

    # "It's not much, but maybe he can do her a little favour? She was talking about wanting to de-stress, right?"
    "No es mucho, pero ¿tal vez pueda hacerla un pequeño favor? Habló de desestresarse, ¿cierto?"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3534
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_8ee4111e:

    # "That's true, but she's not sure what he can do to help her situation and of course he suggests they try hypnosis again." with dissolve
    "Es verdad, pero no está segura de qué puede hacer para ayudar a su situación y, por supuesto, él sugiere intentar con hipnosis otra vez." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3535
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_ac3c0fbc:

    # "He's thought about why he failed last time, and he reckons he's figured it out if she's willing to give it another go."
    "Pensó en por qué falló la última vez, y afirma haberlo descifrado si ella está dispuesta a hacer otro intento."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3538
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_d170dd18:

    # "She agrees, and he directs her to lay on the couch, then attempts a basic relaxation induction, with his words emphasising feeling." with dissolve
    "Ella acepta, y él la invita a recostarse en el sofá, luego intenta una inducción básica de relajación, con palabras que enfatizan sentimiento." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3540
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_d0af9118:

    # "So this would be a departure from the more visual led induction he first tried on her."
    "Esto sería un depurado de la primera inducción que probó en ella, que era más visual."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3541
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_fd5145f9:

    # "This time he appears to be successful, and begins impressing on her that she should feel good and confident about herself."
    "Esta vez, perece que tiene éxito, y comienza a decirle que debería sentirse bien o con confianza en sí misma."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3542
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_5db868b9:

    # "And that she needs to remember always that she's a kind and generous soul and nothing can get her down."
    "Y que siempre debe recordar que tiene un alma dulce y generosa y nada puede derribarla."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3544
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_3a7380e1:

    # "... Or somesuch. It's a little mushy, and Akiko's teary from it when she wakes, but she appreciates what Kyou's trying to do and says she needed someone to tell her that." with dissolve
    "... O algo por el estilo. Es un poco cursi, y Akiko despierta con lágrimas, pero dice que aprecia lo que Kyou intenta hacer y dice que necesitaba que alguien le dijera eso." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3545
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_1f6b5d96:

    # "They share an embrace, and Akiko tells him that no matter what happens, they're both going to get through these hard times one way or another."
    "Se abrazan, y Akiko le dice que no importa lo que pase, ambos superaran estos tiempos difíciles de una forma u otra."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3547
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_706002f4:

    # "And... that's it, I guess? Can we stop it here?"
    "Y... eso es todo, ¿supongo? ¿Podemos parar aquí?"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3548
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_2a7705c7:

    # "So, Kyou did a very bad thing but went above and beyond to right that wrong in the end, so I certainly didn't want this bleak as fuck storyline to end on a downer."
    "Así que, Kyou hizo algo muy malo y fue más allá del bien y el mal al final, así que, ciertamente, no quería que esta jodida y sombría ruta terminara con un bajón."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3549
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_5ce75199:

