translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_0a40d90e:

    # ks "Feel the comforting coolness of the air as you breathe it into your lungs, as you hold your breath now, Akiko. Hold it..."
    ks "Siente la acogedora frescura del aire llenando tus pulmones, y ahora sostén el aliento, Akiko. Sostenlo..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3878
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_6ebebc5a:

    # "I then place my hand gently over the top of her head as I speak my next words." with dissolve
    "Entonces coloco mi mano en la parte de arriba de su cabeza para decir las siguientes palabras." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3846
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_65e85993:

    # ks "And now slowly exhale. As you do so, you can feel a warm wave of relaxation wash over you."
    ks "Y ahora exhala lentamente. Al hacerlo, podrás sentir una cálida ola de relajación recorrer tu cuerpo."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3847
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_83296235:

    # "Falling silent for a moment, I listen as Akiko dutifully exhales; seemingly content to follow along for now."
    "Guardando silencio por un momento, escucho cómo Akiko exhala obedientemente; al parecer contenta de seguirme por ahora."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3848
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_d762c7e9:

    # ks "Feeling that wave travel through your head, weighing down your eyelids with a comfortable sensation of tiredness as it moves down your neck..."
    ks "Siente cómo esa ola viaja por tu cabeza, llenando tus párpados con una cómoda sensación de cansancio, y luego bajando por tu cuello."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3849
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_19b5ea08:

    # ks "Going down your shoulders and chest. Your arms. Your legs... All the way down to your feet and the tips of your toes."
    ks "Pasando por tus hombros y torso. Tus brazos. Tus piernas... Y finalmente tus pies y las puntas de tus dedos."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3886
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_f2ecbc99:

    # "I then pull my hand away and look her over, noting how she seems to be keeping still."
    "Luego retiro mi mano y la observo, notando que parece quedarse quieta."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3851
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_f9e076ea:

    # "Let's see if I can get her to close her eyes this time."
    "Veamos si logro que cierre los ojos esta vez."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3852
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_89a7be42:

    # ks "Very good, Akiko. Allowing yourself to enjoy this feeling of calm. And now, take another breath. Nice and long and deep..."
    ks "Muy bien, Akiko. Disfruta este sentimiento de calma. Y ahora, toma aire una vez más. Lenta y profundamente..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3853
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_cb86f0b8:

    # "Her chest rises as she inhales through her nose, and I wait for her to finish before calmly talking again."
    "Su pecho se eleva al inhalar por la nariz, y espero a que termine antes de seguir hablando."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3854
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_0181210b:

    # ks "Hold it... That's right. Enjoying that comforting feeling of fullness in your lungs for a moment."
    ks "Sostenlo... Eso es. Disfruta esa reconfortante sensación al llenar por un momento tus pulmones."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3855
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_df08a72f:

    # "Then, placing my hand gently on the top of her head again, I continue."
    "Luego, poniendo gentilmente mi mano en su cabeza de nuevo, continúo."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3856
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_ab9c98f3:

    # ks "And breathe out. Feeling another calming, relaxing wave wash over you. All through your head, that wave of comfortable tiredness that invites you to close your eyes..."
    ks "Y exhala. Sintiendo cómo otra relajante ola recorre tu cuerpo. Cómo pasa por tu cabeza esa ola de dulce cansancio que te invita a cerrar los ojos..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3900
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_e36b23e9:

    # "I pause a moment for effect, and Akiko lets her eyes close this time."
    "Hago una pausa por efecto, y Akiko esta vez cierra los ojos."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3859
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_1e2a3279:

    # "Not sure if she feels any more hypnotized, but at least she's comfortable with what we're doing."
    "No sé si se sienta más hipnotizada, pero al menos se siente cómoda con lo que estamos haciendo."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3860
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_306cfc0f:

    # ks "Washing over the rest of your body. Easing all the muscles in your neck and shoulders. Releasing the tension in your spine. Soothing your calves..."
    ks "Extendiéndose por el resto de tu cuerpo. Aflojando cada músculo de tu cuello y hombros. Liberando la tensión de tu columna. Relajando tus piernas."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3861
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_9d6c614c:

    # ks "Leaving your feet feeling light and tingly as that deep wave of relaxation travels through your entire body."
    ks "Haciendo que tus pies se sientan muy ligeros con el paso de esa ola de relajación que viaja por todo tu cuerpo."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3862
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_ca75329a:

    # "Once again, I take my hand off of her and fall silent for a few moments. Just letting her internalize that feeling of calm that I'm impressing on her."
    "Nuevamente, retiro mi mano y guardo silencio por unos momentos. Dejando que internalice esa sensación de calma que le estoy describiendo."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3875
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_889205c8:

    # "But now comes the moment of truth. The part of my script where she's supposed to feel hypnotized."
    "Pero ahora viene el momento de la verdad. La parte del guion en la que se supone que se sient0061 hipnotizada."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3864
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_e5a2addb:

    # ks "Now Akiko, soon you may start to find your conscious mind beginning to wander on its own. And I just want to tell you that's okay. You can let that happen."
    ks "Ahora, Akiko, pronto puede que notes que tu mente consciente comienza a vagar por su cuenta. Y solo quiero decirte que eso está bien."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3877
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_bf9b4c76:

    # ks "Your subconscious mind will still be here, listening and responding, no matter how much your conscious mind wanders. No matter how deeply relaxed you become."
    ks "Tu subconsciente seguirá ahí, escuchando y respondiendo, sin importar cuánto divague tu mente consciente. Sin importar cuán profundamente relajada estés."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3866
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_411e798c:

    # ks "There's no need to worry about it. Now, let's take another deep, long, comforting breath. In..."
    ks "No hay necesidad de preocuparse por eso. Ahora, tomemos aire una vez más, lenta y profundamente. Inhala..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3867
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_d413ff54:

    # "I then place my hand upon her for a third time."
    "Luego coloco mi mano sobre ella una tercera vez."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3868
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_6b56be1d:

    # ks "And slowly out. More relaxation. Feeling your eyelids so comfortably heavy that they won't want to open. Feeling your neck so limp. Shoulders so loose..."
    ks "Y suéltalo lentamente. Más relajación. Sintiendo que tus párpados están tan pesados que no querrán abrirse. Tu cuello muy flojito. Tus hombros sueltos..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3869
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_42cba163:

    # ks "Every muscle in your arms, your fingers, every joint in your body, so completely free of tension now, Akiko..."
    ks "Cada músculo de tus brazos, cada articulación de tu cuerpo, ahora completamente libre de tensión, Akiko..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3870
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_7b4d15c9:

    # "As the breath leaves her body, I raise my hand to leave it hovering just above her head."
    "Una vez el aire sale de su cuerpo, levanto mi mano y la dejo rondando justo arriba de su cabeza."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3871
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_c33c2359:

    # "I was right about having Akiko concentrate on what she feels instead of what she sees. She's responding way better to this kind of induction."
    "Fue buena idea hacer que Akiko se concentrara en lo que siente, en vez de en lo que ve. Está respondiendo mucho mejor a esta clase de inducción."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3872
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_1c55cfdb:

    # "But is she hypnotized?"
    "Pero ¿está hipnotizada?"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3873
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_5dff8977:

    # ks "And now I want you to take another deep, comfortable breath into your lungs, and..."
    ks "Y ahora quiero que vuelvas a respirar muy ondo y..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3874
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_3c73dd01:

    # "Now's the time to find out, as I place my hand back on her head and apply just a little pressure on her scalp with my fingertips."
    "Es momento de averiguarlo. Ahora poso mi mano sobre su cabeza y aplico un poquito de presión en su cabellera con las puntas de mis dedos."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3876
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_892e7540:

    # ks "Breathe out. Feeling that deep, powerful wave of relaxation once more. Allowing your conscious mind to drift peacefully away."
    ks "Exhala. Sintiendo nuevamente esa profunda y poderosa ola de relajación. Dejando que tu mente consciente se desvanezca."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3877
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_258e3161:

    # ks "Allowing me to speak just with your subconscious now. Do you understand, Akiko?"
    ks "Permitiéndome hablar solamente con tu subconsciente. ¿Comprendes, Akiko? "

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3878
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_726e7f4d:

    # "My question lingers as I wonder how she'll react to something that suddenly requires her to respond."
    "Mi pregunta perdura. Me pregunto cómo reaccionará a algo que repentinamente requiere de su respuesta."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3930
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_60a0965a:

    # "And after a few moments I can see her lips twitch uncertainly. Like she's trying to remember how to speak."
    "Y tras unos pocos momentos, veo que sus labios se estremecen. Como si intentara recordar cómo hablar."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3881
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_9b69dc76:

    # a "{size=12}Y... esss...{/size}"
    a "{size=12}S... sssíi...{/size}"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3934
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_b0d6323a:

    # "Man, I can barely make out a noise at all. But it seemed to be in the affirmative."
    "Cielos, apenas logro oírla. Pero parece que fue afirmativo."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3884
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_5f067864:

    # "And the feeling of her own voice, quiet and weak as it was, may have been enough to convince her that things really are different this time."
    "Y la sensación de su propia voz, tan débil y suave, puede que sea suficiente para convencerla de que las cosas son diferentes esta vez."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3885
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_c65a4640:

    # ks "Very good, Akiko. Going deeper into relaxation. Deeper into hypnosis."
    ks "Muy bien, Akiko. Relajante más profundamente. Cayendo más profundo en hipnosis."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3886
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_fa128fa2:

    # "So... I think I've proven to her that she can be hypnotized."
    "Bueno... creo que ya le demostré que puede ser hipnotizada."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3887
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_dc3e8971:

    # ks "And now that you're here, in this deeply hypnotized state of being, there are a few things that I need to say to your subconscious."
    ks "Y ya que estás aquí, en este profundo estado hipnótico, hay un par de cosas que debo decirle a tu subconsciente."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3888
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_62fcbaf4:

    # "Now to prove I can use it to help her."
    "Ahora, a demostrar que puedo usarlo para ayudarla."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3889
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_dc493b22:

    # ks "Things that your subconscious may consider to be true."
    ks "Cosas que tu subconsciente podría considerar ciertas."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3891
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_d62ede7f:

    # ks "Because Akiko, no matter how bad things get, you will always remember that you are a strong and confident woman."
    ks "Porque, Akiko, no importa lo mal que se pongan las cosas, siempre recordarás que eres una mujer fuerte y llena de confianza."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3892
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_dd1dbcf2:

    # ks "No matter what anyone says to bring you down, you know that you are a kind, generous soul and nothing they say can bring you down."
    ks "Sin importar lo que nadie diga para hacerte caer, sabrás que tienes un alma generosa y nada de lo que digan puede derribarte."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3893
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_c4b95d71:

    # a "{size=16}M-mm...{/size}"
    a "{size=16}M-mm...{/size}"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:5368
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_4fcf8747:

    # ks "You deserve to find happiness too."
    ks "Tú también mereces encontrar la felicidad."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3895
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_9b4d580f:

    # "She murmurs, and I can see her lips quiver as I talk."
    "Murmura, y puedo ver que sus labios tiemblan mientras hablo."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3896
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_2076d2d0:

    # ks "Anyway, that's all I wanted to say. So in a few moments I'm going to count up slowly, from one to five."
    ks "Como sea, eso es todo lo que quería decir. En unos momentos voy a contar lentamente, del uno al cinco."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3897
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_2b2a629a:

    # ks "With each number you'll be able to feel yourself becoming more awake and aware, feeling your conscious mind return."
    ks "Con cada número, te sentirás más despierta y alerta, sintiendo como tu mente consciente regresa."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3898
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_d4c104c2:

    # ks "And on five, you will be wide awake and refreshed. Remembering everything, feeling so good about yourself as I count now..."
    ks "Y al llegar a cinco, despertarás sintiéndote fresca. Recordando todo, sintiéndote muy bien contigo misma..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3899
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_aed4f98f:

    # ks "One, just starting to rouse yourself..."
    ks "Uno, comienzas a despertar..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3900
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_c37169d7:

    # ks "Two, feeling your arms and legs and feet beginning to stir..."
    ks "Dos, sintiendo cómo tus brazos y piernas comienzan a moverse..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3901
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_3eb19634:

    # ks "Three, becoming aware of your breathing now. Feeling more awake, more alert."
    ks "Tres, más consciente de tu respiración. Sintiéndote despierta y alerta."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3902
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_15df58a7:

    # ks "Four, taking a nice deep breath now. Feeling your eyelids loosen, and..."
    ks "Cuatro, ahora respira hondo. Sintiendo que tus párpados se aflojan."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3903
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_1343702b:

    # ks "Five. Wide awake and feeling great, Akiko."
    ks "Cinco. Despierta, sintiéndote muy bien, Akiko."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3959
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_5d5b890d:

    # "I watch as her eyes flicker gently back into life."
    "Veo cómo sus ojos vuelven gentilmente a la vida."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3906
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_655ddcef:

    # "As she starts to regain her focus, our gazes meet..."
    "Mientras comienza a recuperar el enfoque, nuestras miradas se cruzan..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3907
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_8ec47439:

    # a cry "*sniffle*" with dissolve
    a cry "*snif*" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3908
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_e79c44de:

    # ks surprised "H-hey, 'Kiko, what's wrong? Are you okay?"
    ks surprised "O-oye, 'Kiko, ¿qué sucede? ¿Te encuentras bien?"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3909
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_53a9ff82:

    # "Shit. The LAST thing I want to do is make her cry!"
    "Mierda. ¡Lo ÚLTIMO que quiero es hacerla llorar!"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3912
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_df9da1e0:

    # "Akiko slides off the couch as she gives me a hasty nod, choking down a sob..."
    "Akiko se levanta del sofá, asintiendo apresuradamente y ahogando un sollozo."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3915
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_e2d2d060:

    # "... before weakly leaning into my shoulder."
    "... para luego colocar débilmente su cabeza en mi hombro."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3970
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_3167aff5:

    # ks casual surprised "'Kiko?"
    ks casual surprised "¿'Kiko?"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3917
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_3cbfdaba:

    # a casual "I-I'm okay! *sniff* I just... w-wow, ahaha!" with dissolve
    a casual "¡E-estoy bien! *snif* Es que... ¡g-guau, jajaja!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3918
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_24e65d84:

    # a cry_smile "I had no idea how much I needed to hear that just now..." with dissolve
    a cry_smile "No tenía idea de cuánto necesitaba oír eso." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3919
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_85681f80:

    # "Tentatively, I put my arms around her, and she responds in kind as we share a quiet embrace."
    "Tentativamente, cierro mis brazos sobre ella, a lo que responde a la par, y compartimos un silencioso abrazo."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3920
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_f32e752d:

    # "Seems things have been rough for both of us. And we've sure made some mistakes, big and small."
    "Parece que las cosas han sido difíciles para ambos. Y está claro que hemos cometido errores, grandes y pequeños."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3921
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_f82e763a:

    # "But right now, in this moment, it doesn't seem so bad."
    "Pero ahora mismo, en este momento, no parece estar tan mal."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3922
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_d480c07a:

    # "I've come a long way, and it feels like Akiko's had a journey of her own."
    "He recorrido un largo sendero, y parece que Akiko también ha tenido su propio viaje."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3923
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_2613f09c:

    # "We have friends like Sayori and Risa, who know who we really are even if the rest of the world seems set against us."
    "Tenemos amigas como Sayori y Risa, que saben quiénes somos realmente, aun cuando el resto del mundo parece estar en nuestra contra."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3924
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_564788f1:

    # "And, at least for the time being, we have each other."
    "Y, al menos por el momento, nos tenemos el uno al otro."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3940
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_215c38fe:

    # a "It's going to be alright, Kyou." with dissolve
    a "Todo estará bien, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3926
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_e0c91582:

    # a happy "You'll see..." with dissolve
    a happy "Ya lo verás..." with dissolve

# TODO: Translation updated at 2021-01-04 21:08

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3798
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_937e287d:

    # a sad_side "Hypnosis? Risa told me you broke that light you had. The light that let you hypnotize people." with dissolve
    a sad_side "¿Hipnosis? Risa me dijo que destruiste tu linterna. La de la luz que te permitía hipnotizar gente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3799
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_c973f6c8:

    # a sad "Was that wrong?" with dissolve
    a sad "¿Estaba equivocada?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3803
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_b917635e:

    # ks neutral "No. I did break the penlight, and that's the reason my hypnosis was able to hurt Hiroko the way it did."
    ks neutral "No. Sí destruí la linterna, y era la razón por la que mi hipnosis fue capaz de hacerle daño a Hiroko de esa forma."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3804
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_af50d18d:

    # ks "But I don't think I need to give up hypnosis because of that."
    ks "Pero no creo que por eso deba renunciar a la hipnosis."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3810
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_4de001e4:

    # a frown "And you know you can't hypnotize me without that light anyway! S-so you'd be wasting your time, and..." with dissolve
    a frown "¡Y de todos modos ya sabes que no puedes hipnotizarme sin esa luz! A-así que estarías perdiendo el tiempo, y..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3904
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_9a980485:

    # ks "No matter what anyone says to hurt you, you know that you are a kind, generous soul and nothing they say can bring you down."
    ks "Sin importar lo que nadie diga para lastimarte, sabrás que tienes un alma dulce y generosa y nada de lo que digan puede derribarte."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3926
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_70acc9d4:

    # "... before weakly leaning in to hug me."
    "... para luego acercarse débilmente y abrazarme."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3933
translate spanish Epilogue_Redemption_Sacrifice_55e8d345:

    # "Tentatively, I put my arms around her, and she tightens her arms around me as we share a quiet embrace." with dissolve
    "Tentativamente, cierro mis brazos sobre ella, luego ella aprieta los suyos con más fuerza, y compartimos un silencioso abrazo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3144
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_774f5607:

    # "As she nods, Nozomi seems to spy the two chairs I have beside me, arranged a couple of feet apart. " with dissolve
    "Asintiendo, Nozomi parece espiar las dos sillas que tengo a mi lado, puestas a poco más de un metro una de la otra." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3145
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_72ac4b90:

    # "She then looks back to Sayori, who smiles back at her calmly while she pops her shoes off."
    "Luego vuelve a mirar a Sayori, quien le sonríe con calma mientras se quita los zapatos."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3416
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_f61a7c87:

