# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2013
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f3836180:

    # ks "That penlight... I still don't know how it happened. And after I broke it, I don't think we'll ever know." with dissolve
    ks "Esa linterna... aún no sé cómo pasó. Y después de destruirla, creo que nunca lo sabremos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2014
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_6d8eec92:

    # ks "It was such a freaky, totally unexpected thing that it'd be weird if we didn't get tempted by what it could do for us."
    ks "Fue algo tan extraño e inesperado que habría sido raro que no nos tentara lo que podía hacer por nosotros."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2015
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e91bd875:

    # ks "But we came out of it, didn't we? That thing's gone, it's never coming back, and... well, we're still here!"
    ks "Pero lo dejamos, ¿no? Esa cosa se ha ido, nunca volverá y... bueno, ¡seguimos aquí!"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2016
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_bdfa7676:

    # ks "We know what hypnosis is supposed to be like. And I think so does your mom, and your friends."
    ks "Sabemos cómo se supone que sea la hipnosis. Y creo que tu mamá también, y tus amigas."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2017
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e07f944c:

    # ks "So please don't be too hard on yourself now. I couldn't bear it if I ruined hypnosis for you."
    ks "Así que, por favor, no seas tan dura contigo. No soportaría haber arruinado la hipnosis para ti."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2019
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_33f795ca:

    # n "..." with dissolve
    n "..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2020
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_afb0d081:

    # n sad_closed "I don't think you ruined it for me, Kyou. I think I might have ruined it for myself." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "No creo que me hayas arruinado la hipnosis, Kyou. Creo que yo la arruiné para mí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2021
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_de303d65:

    # n front sleeptalk_concerned "After everything that happened, I think the love I had for it might actually be gone." with dissolve
    n front sleeptalk_concerned "Después de todo lo que pasó, creo que el amor que tenía por la hipnosis tal vez se haya ido." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2022
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d105af0a:

    # ks smirk "Are you sure that's true, Nozomi?"
    ks smirk "¿Estás segura de que eso es cierto, Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2023
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2c950010:

    # n neutral "Why wouldn't it be true?" with dissolve
    n neutral "¿Por qué no sería cierto?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2024
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c89976fc:

    # "Yeah, what happened is still getting her down, but from what we've been through together I have a good feeling she'll appreciate what I'm about to do for her."
    "Sí, lo que ocurrió aún la deprime, pero por lo que hemos pasado juntos, tengo el presentimiento de que apreciará lo que estoy por hacer."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2025
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a51c62be:

    # ks smile "Well, here's a way to find out for sure. Put your hands together like this."
    ks smile "Bueno, hay una forma de averiguarlo. Junta tus manos así."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2027
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_04758dd6:

    # "I hold my hands together in front of me and Nozomi, after a pause, starts to mimic me." with dissolve
    "Coloco mis manos juntas frente a mí y Nozomi, tras una pausa, comienza a imitarme." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2028
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c6633d52:

    # ks "Now hold them up in front of your face and extend your pointer fingers out, nice and straight."
    ks "Ahora ponlas frente a tu rostro y levanta los índices. Ponlos muy firmes."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2032
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_cd1f1bb5:

    # n "... I don't know what this is supposed to prove."
    n "... No sé qué probará esto."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2033
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_8f05e3a3:

    # k "You know you can stop this at any time. You can certainly try to. Or you might find yourself staring at that space in-between your fingers. Right here where I'm pointing."
    k "Sabes que puedes parar en cualquier momento. Puedes intentarlo. O puedes mirar el espacio que hay entre tus dedos. Justo aquí donde estoy señalando."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2032
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d3da7354:

    # "Nozomi's eyes turn to focus on the spot between her pointed fingers. And immediately I start to take the finger I pointed with and begin to circle it around her hands." with dissolve
    "Los ojos de Nozomi se enfocan en el punto que hay entre sus dedos. E inmediatamente empiezo a trazar un círculo alrededor de sus manos con el mismo dedo que usé para señalar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2036
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_779a7f8b:

    # k "You can try to pull your eyes away, or you may now find a growing force pushing your fingertips towards each other. Pushing harder and harder."
    k "Puedes intentar desviar la mirada, o puedes sentir esa fuerza de atracción que jala tus dedos uno contra el otro. Tirando más y más fuerte."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2036
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_3fdf8c63:

    # n "Mmn..."
    n "Mmn..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2037
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7611b12e:

    # "My finger continues to circle, while Nozomi's start to quiver as she stares intently."
    "Mi dedo continúa dando vueltas, mientras que Nozomi comienza a temblar, observando intensamente."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2038
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7485f1b0:

    # "She knows what I'm doing, and she knows she can stop playing this game with me any time she likes. I don't have that penlight anymore."
    "Sabe lo que estoy haciendo, y sabe que puede dejar este juego cuando desee. Ya no tengo esa linterna."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2039
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_75dca87e:

    # "And yet, in spite of that..."
    "Y sin embargo, a pesar de eso..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2045
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4ee1e170:

    # k "That force becoming more and more powerful, pushing those fingertips of yours closer and closer..."
    k "Esa fuerza se vuelve más y más poderosa, acercando tus dedos más y más..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2041
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_91ee704b:

    # "Nozomi is finding she wants this after all."
    "Nozomi descubre que quiere esto después de todo."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2050
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_10db20b7:

    # k "And you can try to resist. You can try to pull your fingers away, but the more you try, the stronger the force becomes."
    k "Y puedes intentar resistir. Puedes intentar separar tus dedos, pero entre más lo intentas, más fuerte se vuelve esa atracción."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2051
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_bac4087d:

    # k "The more you try, the stronger it becomes and the deeper you'll fall into hypnosis the moment they touch."
    k "Entre más lo intentas, se vuelve más fuerte y caerás más profundo en hipnosis en cuanto se junten."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2054
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7cdf6ac0:

    # k "{cps=20}Keeping your feet planted firmly on the ground, staying perfectly upright even when your fingertips touch... {/cps}{w=1.0}and {nw}"
    k "{cps=20}Con los pies firmes en el suelo, perfectamente erguida incluso cuando tus dedos se juntan... {/cps}{w=1.0}y {nw}"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2048
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_5eefdcb7:

    # extend "sleep!"
    extend "¡duerme!"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2049
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_62cbee3c:

    # "I snap my fingers just as Nozomi helplessly touches her tips together, and man am I happy that worked."
    "Chasqueo mis dedos justo cuando las yemas de Nozomi hacen contacto, y cielos, cuánto me alegra que haya funcionado."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2065
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_eb9bf408:

    # k "Going deeper into this pleasant state of hypnotic trance. Allowing yourself to enjoy this feeling, allowing yourself to relax all the way while staying nice and upright."
    k "Y cae más y más profundo en este placentero estado de trance hipnótico. Disfrutando este sentimiento. Completamente relajada mientras permaneces de pie."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2066
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_5f4b2712:

    # "It was a simple hypnotic induction, of course. So simple even Hiroko could do it."
    "Fue una inducción hipnótica simple, por supuesto. Tan simple que hasta Hiroko podría hacerla."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2067
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2c0d5afc:

    # k "Because you do enjoy this, don't you, Nozomi?"
    k "Porque disfrutas esto, ¿no es así, Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2053
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f0c0ff95:

    # n sleeptalk "{size=16}Ye... y-yeah...{/size}" with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "{size=16}S-... s-sí...{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2055
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c2e34d47:

    # "But it's all I needed to show Nozomi that her love of hypnosis is as strong as ever." with dissolve
    "Pero solo eso necesito para mostrarle a Nozomi que su amor por la hipnosis es tan fuerte como siempre." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2072
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_71c2f651:

    # k "Of course you do. And when I count up to three and snap my fingers you're going to wake up from this trance, happy and refreshed."
    k "Por supuesto que sí. Y cuando cuente hasta tres y chasquee mis dedos, despertarás de este trance, fresca y contenta."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2073
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_1f9173f3:

    # k "And what's more, when we arrive back in class and until it's time to close the café you're going to become the best maid this school has ever seen."
    k "Y además, cuando regresemos al salón y hasta que sea hora de cerrar el café, te convertirás en la mejor sirvienta que esta escuela haya visto."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2075
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f6b2c36e:

    # k "You'll be friendly, happy and eager to help our customers so they'll all leave with smiles on their faces. Okay?" with dissolve
    k "Serás amable, alegre y estarás feliz de ayudar a los clientes para que salgan con una sonrisa en sus rostros. ¿Muy bien?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2059
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_064b9d68:

    # n sleeptalk "Okay..." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "Bien..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2079
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_78386c43:

    # k "{cps=15}One, two, three, and {/cps}{nw}" with dissolve
    k "{cps=15}Uno, dos, tres y {/cps}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2083
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d9e06b1c:

    # extend "wide awake!"
    extend "¡despierta!"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2066
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_3f2ab955:

    # "Nozomi lets her eyelids open slowly as I step back and watch her in the autumn sun."
    "Nozomi abre sus ojos lentamente, y yo doy un paso atrás para observarla bajo el sol del otoño."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2067
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_6955d662:

    # "It's only just now I realize it's been a while since I thought this... but she really is beautiful."
    "Y ahora me doy cuenta de cuánto ha pasado desde que pensé esto... pero es realmente hermosa."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2068
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a6adc57f:

    # "I guess that's weird. But after all this time I've really just liked that we've been able to hang out together like this."
    "Es raro. Pero luego de todo este tiempo simplemente me ha gustado el haber podido pasar tiempo con ella."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2093
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_3f20d00d:

    # "And it sure feels amazing, being able to put that smile on her face."
    "Y se siente maravilloso poder dibujar esa sonrisa en su rostro."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2096
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_add87a4e:

    # n "S-so, I guess we should head back now, huh?"
    n "P-pues, creo que ya hay que regresar, ¿no?"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2099
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2f6b4e39:

    # k "Yeah. The class needs its star maid back."
    k "Sí. La clase necesita a su sirvienta estrella."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2101
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_afd4e3f3:

    # n "Ahahaha~" with dissolve
    n "Ajajajaja." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2074
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0a6a66c7:

    # n smile "Well... w-we'll see about that~" with dissolve
    n smile "Bueno... e-eso ya lo veremos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2076
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_1e7f9f74:

    # "She walks with a spring back in her step as she heads back inside." with dissolve
    "Avanza con renovada alegría, camino a las aulas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2077
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a7989259:

    # "And as I follow behind her, I have a feeling this afternoon's gonna be a lot more fun for everyone."
    "Y al caminar detrás de ella, tengo el presentimiento de que esta tarde será mucho más divertida para todos."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2079
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_fdbb7bbf:

    # "May we have many more days like this..."
    "Tengamos muchos más días así..."
# TODO: Translation updated at 2021-09-28 21:08

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:2563
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_038b5594:

    # n "Today did seem a little pointless, didn't it."
    n "Lo de hoy fue un poco inútil, ¿no?"

# TODO: Translation updated at 2021-10-15 22:51

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3024
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_df0e3c99_3:

    # "As another school day draws to a close, I gather my things and ponder."
    "Con el cierre de otro día de escuela, guardo mis cosas mientras reflexiono."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3031
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_5c5a0c53:

    # h "Man, why'd they even make us come to school today. We didn't do shit." with dissolve
    h "Caray, ¿para qué nos hicieron venir a la escuela hoy? No hicimos una mierda." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3032
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_9bea8cb9_2:

    # "It's been a couple of months since that day."
    "Han pasado un par de meses desde aquel día."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3034
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_7a3628ba:

    # s uniform_handup alert_irritated "We are in a post-examination wilderness. It was inevitable that we would have little to do." with dissolve
    s uniform_handup alert_irritated "Estamos en un yermo port-exámenes. Era inevitable que tuviéramos poco que hacer." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3035
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_52b57127:

    # "A couple months since I messed around with that penlight and gave Sayori an alternate personality."
    "Un par de meses desde que usé esa linterna y le di a Sayori una personalidad alternativa."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3036
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_8757aaaf:

    # n smile_side "It is what it is. But now we're about to get a lot busier, huh?" with dissolve
    n smile_side "Es lo que es. Pero hoy vamos a estar mucho más ocupadas, ¿eh?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3037
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_021005c6:

    # h uniform_armup happy "Hells yeah! The weekend starts here~" with dissolve
    h uniform_armup happy "¡Pues claro! Ya es fin de semana." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3038
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_590562ad:

    # "I destroyed the penlight after all the trouble it caused. But even so, Sayori wanted me to leave her alone while she \"dealt with the consequences of my decision\"."
    "Destruí la linterna después de todos los problemas que causó. Pero a pesar de ello, Sayori quiso que la dejara sola mientras ella \"lidiaba con las consecuencias de mi decisión\"."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3040
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_0a868f51:

    # h happy_side "You with me, sis?" with dissolve
    h happy_side "¿Estás conmigo, hermana?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3041
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_951f9a1b:

    # "I'd want to at least ask how she's been dealing with things since the incident but, well..."
    "Me gustaría al menos preguntarle cómo ha llevado las cosas desde el incidente, pero, bueno..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3042
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_3fe6c534:

    # s alert_concerned_right "Personally I see little to celebrate, but... I did promise you all." with dissolve
    s alert_concerned_right "Personalmente veo poco que celebrar, pero... les hice una promesa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3043
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_69c3abcf:

    # "... I kind of already know."
    "... Supongo que ya lo sé."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3046
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_458921a9:

    # n happy "So, shall we go?" with dissolve
    n happy "Entonces, ¿vamos?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3047
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_f6b7b4ae:

    # s uniform alert_neutral "One moment. There's that other promise I made to someone." with dissolve
    s uniform alert_neutral "Un momento. Hay otra promesa que le hice a alguien más." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3049
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_08725a7e:

    # n neutral_side "Oh. Right, of course." with dissolve
    n neutral_side "Oh. Claro, por supuesto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3050
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_6a6ec41e:

    # s alert_concerned "Yes. I'm going to talk to him; I shall just be a moment." with dissolve
    s alert_concerned "Sí. Voy a hablar con él; será solo un momento." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3051
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_c3be1023:

    # s alert_neutral_right "... Kyou?" with dissolve
    s alert_neutral_right "... ¿Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3056
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_21d2de5f:

    # ks surprised "H-huh?! What?!" with dissolve
    ks surprised "¡¿E-eh?! ¡¿Qué?!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3057
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_8c6b8e32:

    # "Sayori just sighs at me as I react to her approaching my desk."
    "Sayori simplemente suspira ante mi reacción al acercarse a mi escritorio."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3058
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_f2778bca:

    # s uniform_folded alert_rolleyes "Oh, drop the faux surprised act. We know perfectly well that you eavesdrop on our conversations." with dissolve
    s uniform_folded alert_rolleyes "Oh, no finjas sorpresa. Sabemos perfectamente que escuchas nuestras conversaciones a escondidas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3059
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_88846fac:

    # "I mean... yeah, I kinda know what's going on. The three of them are having a karaoke night to unwind now that our entrance exams are done with."
    "Pues... sí, realmente ya sé lo que está pasando. Las tres tendrán una noche de karaoke para relajarse ahora que los exámenes de admisión terminaron."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3061
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_a0faab1d:

    # h uniform_headhold2 "H'yeah, just like we all know you ain't doing shit tonight." with dissolve
    h uniform_headhold2 "Seh, y también sabemos todos que no tienes una mierda que hacer esta noche." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3062
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_7831dd80:

    # ks sigh "Yeah. And I thought you'd prefer it that way."
    ks sigh "Seh. Y pensé que eso preferirías."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3063
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_b12b0f00:

    # s alert_annoyed_right "You would be correct." with dissolve
    s alert_annoyed_right "Estás en lo correcto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3065
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_98a93792:

    # s alert_irritated "{size=16}... What? No, that was not mean of me to say. I was merely being matter of fact with...{/size}" with dissolve
    s alert_irritated "{size=16}... ¿Qué? No, eso no es lo que quise decir. Simplemente estaba señalando que...{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3066
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_6c75ab8b:

    # "After muttering to herself for a moment more, Sayori lets out another sigh."
    "Tras murmurar para sus adentros un momento más, Sayori suelta otro suspiro."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3067
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_06e380a7:

    # s alert_neutral_right "Kyou, you know better than anyone that it is not solely down to me these days." with dissolve
    s alert_neutral_right "Kyou, tú sabes mejor que nadie que no depende solo de mí estos días." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3068
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_074fa391:

    # ks neutral "Yeah..."
    ks neutral "Sí..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3069
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_0f266bde:

    # s uniform alert_sleeptalk "So... look, I am not going to sugarcoat this. To me, you will always be the man who ruined my life. Just as you will always be the man who saved hers." with dissolve
    s uniform alert_sleeptalk "Así que... mira, no voy a suavizarlo. Para mí, tú siempre serás el hombre que arruinó mi vida. Así como siempre serás el hombre que salvó la suya." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3075
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_d9505f18:

    # s alert_concerned_right "And she would appreciate it very much if you joined us tonight." with dissolve
    s alert_concerned_right "Y sería de su gran aprecio si te nos unieras hoy." with dissolve

