translate spanish TennisBot_Epilogue2_e80e6660:

    # h sleeptalk "I ain't gonna be distracted by all those humans. I only wanna play tennis, 'cuz that's what I do. It's my primary function." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk "No me distraeré con todos esos humanos. Solo quiero jugar tenis, porque a eso me dedico. Es mi función principal." with dissolve

