# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:5858
translate spanish TennisBot_Epilogue2_844ec528:

    # k "We're poor now, but you'll set things right. And I'll support you every step of the way."
    k "Somos pobres ahora, pero tú arreglarás las cosas. Y yo te apoyaré en cada paso del camino."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:5859
translate spanish TennisBot_Epilogue2_7d27f628:

    # k "We're in this crummy place now but s-soon, we'll be jet-setting all over the world. And you'll be playing in all the tournaments I sign you up for."
