# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:5860
translate spanish TennisBot_Epilogue2_d993d2f3:

    # k "I'll manage your finances, your public appearances, and all you need to do is play, just like you've always wanted. You won't have to worry about a thing."
    k "Manejaré tus finanzas, tus apariciones públicas, y todo lo que tú tienes que hacer es jugar, tal como siempre has querido. No tendrás que preocuparte por nada."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:5862
translate spanish TennisBot_Epilogue2_bc7c96ba:

