    "{cps=15}Necesito... ¿quitármela de encima? ¿Detenerla? Pero...{/cps}{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:1420
translate spanish Epilogue_Villain_Devoted_Girlfriend_b6f70b58:

    # n "Stare and let your mind drift. Let your mind..."
    n "Observa y deja que tu mente se apague. Deja que tu mente..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:1423
translate spanish Epilogue_Villain_Devoted_Girlfriend_eb43f3db:

    # n "... Sink. Take a deep breath, stare and sink..."
    n "... se hunda. Respira profundo, observa y déjate llevar..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:1426
translate spanish Epilogue_Villain_Devoted_Girlfriend_aa5caa2b:

    # "{cps=15}I can't... I can't... think-{/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"
    "{cps=15}No puedo... no puedo... pensar-{/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:1429
translate spanish Epilogue_Villain_Devoted_Girlfriend_253bd498:

    # n "Deeper and deeper. Let every thought fade from your beautiful mind..."
    n "Más y más profundo. Deja que todo pensamiento se desvanezca de tu hermosa mente..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:1432
translate spanish Epilogue_Villain_Devoted_Girlfriend_efccfaf5:

    # "I..."
    "Me..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:1435
translate spanish Epilogue_Villain_Devoted_Girlfriend_6b914f3b:

    # n "Feeling so good. Feeling so right."
    n "Se siente muy relajante. Se siente muy bien."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:1438
translate spanish Epilogue_Villain_Devoted_Girlfriend_4301046d:

    # "I feel so good..."
    "Me siento bien..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:1439
translate spanish Epilogue_Villain_Devoted_Girlfriend_d90e14ee:

    # n "And as you start to sink so deep. As you let every thought go, you'll find yourself hearing only my voice."
    n "Y mientras te dejas llevar más profundo, y permites que todos tus pensamientos se vayan, escucharás mi voz."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:1470
translate spanish Epilogue_Villain_Devoted_Girlfriend_98e30818:

    # n "You'll only need me, Kyou. I'll be the only one who can make you feel special. No one else will do." with dissolve
    n "Solo me necesitarás a mí, Kyou. Seré la única que te podrá hacer sentir especial. Nadie más podrá." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:1445
translate spanish Epilogue_Villain_Devoted_Girlfriend_083b9b6c:

    # n "No one else will ever love you like I do. No one else will ever be able to make you feel this good. And very soon you're going to understand that."
    n "Nadie más te amará como yo. Nadie más podrá hacerte sentir así de bien. Y pronto vas a entenderlo."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:1448
translate spanish Epilogue_Villain_Devoted_Girlfriend_fd00cdd1:

    # n "So now that you're so completely relaxed with me. Now that you're reaching that most delicious state of hypnotic trance for me..."
    n "Y ahora que estás completamente relajado. Ahora que estás en este delicioso estado de trance hipnótico..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:1450
translate spanish Epilogue_Villain_Devoted_Girlfriend_45dbd85a:

    # n "You'll let your dreamy eyes close, and sink even deeper for your girlfriend."
    n "Dejarás que tus soñolientos ojos se cierren, y te hundirás aún más profundo mientras tu novia te guía."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:1452
translate spanish Epilogue_Villain_Devoted_Girlfriend_b4d51653:

    # n "That's right. Going deeper. And deeper."
    n "Eso es. Más y más profundo."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:1453
translate spanish Epilogue_Villain_Devoted_Girlfriend_c1b3021b:

    # n "It's going to be just you and me. We'll be together forever."
    n "Seremos solo tú y yo. Estaremos juntos por siempre."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:1454
translate spanish Epilogue_Villain_Devoted_Girlfriend_83aab9e0:

    # n "No one will ever come between me and my boyfriend again..."
    n "Nadie nunca se interpondrá entre mi novio y yo nunca más..."

