# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3677
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_9ed39033:

    # "It's been a few weeks since that day."
    "Han pasado un par de semanas desde aquel día."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3682
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a7f5c82b:

    # n "... As you begin to pace through these twisted corridors the light from your torches suddenly seem dimmer, barely penetrating the inky darkness in which you find yourselves."
    n "... Mientras se adentran a estos retorcidos corredores, la luz de sus antorchas súbitamente parece menguarse, apenas capaz de penetrar la densa oscuridad que los rodea."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3683
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e64040b1:

    # "A few weeks since I messed around with that penlight, and with Sayori's mind."
    "Un par de semanas desde que le hice alteraciones a esa linterna, y a la mente de Sayori."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3684
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_7d68ca5b:

    # h "Huh? What's with the lights? I wanna do, like, a perceiving roll!"
    h "¿Eh? ¿Qué onda con las luces? ¡Voy a hacer un, este, tiro de percepción!"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3685
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_62920a8e:

    # "I don't know why I'm thinking about that now, though."
    "Aunque no sé por qué estoy pensando en eso ahora."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3687
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_7d436c0e:

    # n "Sure... okay, as your eyes try to adjust you can only conclude that this darkness that envelops you is magical in nature."
    n "Claro... de acuerdo, mientras sus ojos intentan ajustarse, solo pueden concluir que esta oscuridad que los envuelve es de naturaleza mágica."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3688
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_c5d7d471:

    # "It was a crazy time for sure. An experience that changed mine and Sayori's lives, yet..."
    "Sin duda fue una locura. Una experiencia que cambió mi vida y la de Sayori, y sin embargo..."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3689
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_4de738b9:

    # h "Oh, I get it. Hey, wiz, you wanna help us out here? We can't see shit."
    h "Oh, ya entiendo. Oye, maguito, ¿una ayudita aquí? No vemos una mierda."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3690
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_23f31c94:

    # "... These past few weeks might have been even crazier?"
    "... ¿Puede que estas últimas semanas hayan sido todavía más locas?"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3697
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_9d6ab682:

    # h "HEY, EARTH TO WIZ, WE GOTTA PROBLEM HERE!" with vpunch
    h "¡EY, TIERRA A MAGUITO, TENEMOS UN PROBLEMA AQUÍ!" with vpunch

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3699
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_28c0c94f:

    # "But I guess that's enough reminiscing. I gotta get my head back in this."
    "Pero creo que ya es suficiente retrospectiva. Debo devolver mi cabeza al juego."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3703
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e4890868:

    # ks casual frown "Oh what's this? The young magephobe desires my aid now?" with dissolve
    ks casual frown "Oh, ¿qué es esto? ¿La joven hechizerofóbica desea mi ayuda ahora?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3704
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d8248db0:

    # "I gotta get in character."
    "Debo meterme en personaje."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3705
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_3590a926:

    # h annoyed "I don't \"desire\" shit from you, I just wanna get a move on in this castle an' it's about time you were good for something." with dissolve
    h annoyed "Yo no \"deseo\" una mierda de ti, solo quiero entrar a ese castillo y ya va siendo hora de que sirvas de algo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3706
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_fd9dd67a:

    # h angry "So like, do your fucking job, okay?" with dissolve
    h angry "Así que, o sea, haz tu puto trabajo, ¿sí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3707
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_06bcb93f:

    # "No way in hell am I letting this pipsqueak upstage me in a goddamn roleplaying game, that's for sure."
    "De ninguna forma dejaré que esta pequeñina me pase por encima en un maldito juego de rol."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3710
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_2bfa40af:

    # ks casual frown "I am Shou Long, master of the blazing arts, and I will not be disrespected by some upstart assassin from the Shadow Clan."
    ks casual frown "Yo soy Shou Long, maestro de las artes resplandecientes, y no me faltará al respeto una asesina presuntuosa del clan Sombra."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3711
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_41411633:

    # h rolleyes "Master of time-wasting, more like. You spell chuckers are all the same; buncha arrogant dickheads." with dissolve
    h rolleyes "Más bien maestro de la pérdida de tiempo. Ustedes lanza-hechizos son todos iguales; un montón de pendejos arrogantes." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3713
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b556cc4c:

    # h dungaree_armup irritated "An' I don't care how hot you think you are, you DON'T wanna make enemies of the fuckin' Shadow Clan, 'kay?" with dissolve
    h dungaree_armup irritated "Y no me importa lo poderoso que te creas, NO querrás ser enemigo del puto clan Sombra, ¿de acuerdo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3714
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_519b935e:

    # ks "Such insolence. I command the fires of hell itself, and I will not be talked down to by a mere purveyor of knife tricks."
    ks "Qué insolencia. Yo comando las llamas del infierno mismo, y no me menospreciará una simple proveedora de trucos con cuchillos."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3716
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_5af485df:

    # ks "You call me \"wiz\" again and I'll illuminate these halls with your hair." with dissolve
    ks "Llámame \"maguito\" una vez más e iluminaré estos pasillos con tu cabello." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3715
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_8037bcab:

    # h "Oh, you wanna throw down, huh? Fuck yeah, let's do this!" with dissolve
    h "Oh, pues éntrale, voy a hacerte mierda." with dissolve

