translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_3454cbb7:

    # n pout "Um, not to get in your way, but the darkness you're in is going to incur some heavy accuracy penalties to your dice rolls if you try anything." with dissolve
    n pout "Em, no quisiera entrometerme, pero la oscuridad en la que se encuentran causará fuertes penalizaciones de precisión en sus dados si intentan algo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3719
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_5734d687:

    # ks sigh "That may be a chance I'm willing to take if I get to set her on fire."
    ks sigh "Estoy dispuesto a aceptar las probabilidades si puedo prenderle el cabello en llamas."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3722
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_2ccecf22:

    # h annoyed_side "Gawd, I wanna stab this dude so fuckin' muuuuch." with dissolve
    h annoyed_side "Ay, cómo me dan ganas de apuñalar a este cabrón." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3723
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_4aff4285:

    # ks frown "In the game, you mean?"
    ks frown "En el juego, ¿verdad?"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3724
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_87ae52cd:

    # h dungaree annoyed "... Dude, you had to ask?" with dissolve
    h dungaree annoyed "... Viejo, ¿tenías que preguntar?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3729
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d8577f79:

    # s "Roko, Shou, contain yourselves. Your people may have suffered much at each other's hands, but we can ill afford this bickering if we are to obtain the fortune stone." with dissolve
    s "Roko, Shou, concentraos. Vuestros pueblos han sufrido mucho de la mano del otro, pero no podemos permitirnos tales disputas si hemos de adquirir la piedra de la fortuna." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:4682
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_8c0c6024:

    # s "The townsfolk are depending on us, so let us keep them in our hearts, and cast our grievances and egos aside for their sake!" with dissolve
    s "¡Los ciudadanos dependen de nosotros, así que confinémoslos en nuestros corazones, y hagamos a un lado nuestros agravios y egos por su bien!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3733
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_adc5f761:

    # h smile_side "You're talking about all the reward money when we bring it back, right?" with dissolve
    h smile_side "Hablas del dinero de la recompensa cuando la traigamos de vuelta, ¿verdad?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3735
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e1c0f868:

    # s "Well... The local lord has promised us a substantial bounty on the stone's return, it is true, but as for his motivations for the town..." with dissolve
    s "Bueno... el caudillo local nos ha prometido un botín substancial por el retorno de la piedra, es verdad, mas en lo que respecta a sus motivaciones para el pueblo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3737
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_0bd3b070:

    # ks smile "Fine, fine, enough messing around. I want to cast dispell magic now, Nozomi." with dissolve
    ks smile "Está bien, está bien, basta de tonterías. Quiero lanzar un hechizo de dispersión." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3737
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_2fcd1018:

    # n smile "Alright. So Shou casts his spell and the magical darkness recedes, revealing the way forward." with dissolve
    n smile "Muy bien. Entonces Shou lanza su hechizo y la oscuridad mágica se esfuma, desvelando el camino." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3739
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_5463ed09:

    # n frown "However, it seems you are not alone. You all hear an ominous chittering noise coming from just ahead, and it's getting louder and louder." with dissolve
    n frown "Sin embargo, tal parece que no están solos. Escuchan un nefasto sonido chirriante delante de ustedes, y se vuelve más y más fuerte." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3743
