    # h dungaree irritated "Oh goddammit, is it those fuckin' mind melters again? I'm gonna hurl." with dissolve
    h dungaree irritated "Oh, maldita sea, ¿son los putos derrite-mentes otra vez? Voy a vomitar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3741
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_55b70c62:

    # n sleeptalk "You can't tell from the noise alone. All you know is that it's getting closer." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "No pueden saberlo solo con el sonido. Solo saben que se está acercando." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3742
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_4c01e1a0:

    # h annoyed_side "H'yeah, it's gonna be mind melters." with dissolve
    h annoyed_side "Seh, van a ser derrite-mentes." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3749
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a96de676:

    # s "How bothersome. Perhaps they were attracted to the commotion you and Shou caused arguing just now." with dissolve
    s "Vaya molestia. Quizá fueron atraídos por la conmoción que tú y Shou causaron con su discusión." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3745
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_237ef264:

    # n chuckle "Mhmhm, who can say?" with dissolve
    n chuckle "Jejeje, ¿quién sabe?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3748
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_76a7095b:

    # ks frown "Pretty sure *you* can, Nozomi. You're the one inflicting this on us." with dissolve
    ks frown "Supongo que *tú* sabrás, Nozomi. Eres tú quien está infligiendo esto en nosotros." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3749
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_bb08e2f1:

    # n smile "Me? I'm but an impartial guide to the fantasy land. Anyway, the chittering is becoming even louder, surely they're almost upon you!" with dissolve
    n smile "¿Yo? Yo solo soy una guía imparcial a la tierra de fantasía. En fin, el chirrido se vuelve más y más fuerte, ¡ya casi los tienen encima!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3750
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_60708625:

    # h dungaree_armup angry_side "Alrighty! I draw my daggers and activate my combat stance!" with dissolve
    h dungaree_armup angry_side "¡Muy bien, pues! ¡Saco mis dagas y activo mi posición de combate!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3751
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_761bc01d:

    # ks frown "I prepare a fireball spell."
    ks frown "Yo preparo un hechizo de bola de fuego."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3760
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_0603f052:

    # s "I shall place my flute to my lips and play the melody of tranquility." with dissolve
    s "Yo colocaré mi flauta en mis labios y tocaré la melodía de la tranquilidad." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3754
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_25de547c:

    # n frown "Alright. As our heroes make ready, the chittering noise reaches a fever pitch. From the shadows emerge three large, distinctive forms, their eyes burning with evil intent." with dissolve
    n frown "Muy bien. Nuestros héroes se preparan y el chirrido alcanza su punto culminante. De las sombras, emergen tres grandes y distintivas siluetas con ardiente maldad en sus ojos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3763
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d7a3f8b5:

    # n irritated "{cps=16}And now, brave adventurers, you stand facing the wrath of the deadly and merciless-{/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"
    n irritated "{cps=16}Y ahora, valientes aventureros, encararán la ira de los letales y despiadados-{/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3762
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_54c94156:

    # multi casual frown "Mind melters." with dissolve
    multi casual frown "Derrite-mentes." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3763
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_1bc1cc50:

    # n pout "Well... Technically they're Orthopterrors, but yes, you got me." with dissolve
    n pout "Bueno... Técnicamente son ortropterrores, pero sí, acertaron." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3764
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d5705b5e:

    # n concerned "Gosh, is this campaign really that predictable?" with dissolve
    n concerned "Cielos, ¿en serio esta campaña es tan predecible?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3774
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a5e3fd6d:

    # s "Given what we have gleaned from the campaign master? I have to wonder." with dissolve
    s "¿Dado lo que hemos aprendido de la maestra de campaña? Puede ser." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3767
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_653c9f35:

    # h annoyed_side "Sides, what else is supposed to make a chitterin' noise around here?" with dissolve
    h annoyed_side "Aparte, ¿qué otra cosa hay que haga chirridos?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3768
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e64618d1:

    # n smile "Hehe. Well, they all approach and begin casting confusion on the party. But since Sayori was smart enough to play her melody you all have a plus five on your saving rolls." with dissolve
    n smile "Jeje. Bueno, se aproximan y les aplican el efecto de confusión. Pero ya que Sayori fue astuta y tocó su melodía, tienen cinco puntos extra en sus dados." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3780
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_14b9e76a:

    # s "Who is this \"Sayori\" you speak of? I am Yllaphyra Ashpetal, the bard of Thimhaven." with dissolve
    s "¿Quién es esa tal \"Sayori\" de la que hablas? Yo soy Yllaphyra Ashpetal, bardo de Thimhaven." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3770
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_5217a001:

    # "I can't help but let out a wry chuckle."
    "No puedo evitar reírme."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3783
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_45b87f8e:

    # s "My, what could possibly be funny at a time like this, Shou Long?" with dissolve
    s "Cielos, ¿qué podrá ser tan gracioso en un momento como este, Shou Long?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3784
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b37c4220:

    # ks smirk "Oh, I think you know."
    ks smirk "Oh, creo que lo sabes."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3775
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a14bd140:

    # "\"Yllaphyra\" grins as she takes the twenty-sided die in her hand and rolls it across the table."
    "\"Yllaphyra\" toma el dado de veinte lados en su mano con una sonrisa y lo rueda por la mesa."

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3788
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_54f54e00:

    # s "Mhmhm, perhaps. At least my state of mind is healthier this time, both in and out of the game it seems." with dissolve
    s "Jijiji, quizás. Por lo menos mi estado mental está más sano esta vez, tanto dentro como fuera del juego, al parecer." with dissolve

# game/Kyou Epilogue.rpy:3777
translate spanish Epilogue_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_0bf8832e:

